Package: censeg
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Segregation Measures from Census Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Neal","Marquez",role=c("aut","cre","cph"),email="nmarquez@uw.edu"))
Author: Neal Marquez [aut, cre, cph]
Maintainer: Neal Marquez <nmarquez@uw.edu>
Description: Calculates segregation measures from US census data provided
    through the Census API and accessed in R using the tidycensus package.
